	<purpose>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the representation of validity domains for product or activity data.
	</purpose>
	<inscope>
		<li>identification of a validity domain;</li>
		<li>identification of a validity domain as an interval of serial numbers;</li>
		<li>identification of a validity domain as an interval of time;</li>
		<li>identification of a validity domain as a batch lot of product;</li>
		<li>definition of a relationship between two validity domains.</li>
	</inscope>
